Shadow DOM + Selenium 4



1. Locate Shadow Host
2. Use getShadowRoot()

Note:
XPath is not supported inside ShadowRoot.
Prefer CSS Selectors.

3. Store in SearchContext
4. Use CSS Selectors to locate elements

WebElement host = driver.findElement(By.cssSelector("#shadow-root"));
SearchContext shadowRoot = host.getShadowRoot();
WebElement ele = shadowRoot.findElement(By.cssSelector("span"));


